5
00:00:16,429 --> 00:00:18,910
In his mind, he’s somehow rebutting your
argument.

6
00:00:18,910 --> 00:00:22,760
However, what he’s done is essentially twisted
what you said into something that you didn’t

7
00:00:22,760 --> 00:00:26,740
say, and now he’s attacking his own little
constructed argument.

8
00:00:26,739 --> 00:00:31,570
You tell him that you were thinking more along
the lines of nuts and seeds, but for some

9
00:00:31,570 --> 00:00:40,409
reason, he continues to be very angry with
you.

10
